+# PerpSignals (Bootstrap)
+
+**Ziel**: Public‑Daten von Perpetual‑Futures (ohne API‑Keys) einsammeln, Signale erzeugen, Artefakte unter `docs/`.
+
+## Quickstart (Windows/Powershell)
+```powershell
+python -m venv .venv
+.\.venv\Scripts\activate
+python -m pip install --upgrade pip
+pip install -r requirements.txt -r requirements-dev.txt
+pip install -e .
+python -m pre_commit install
+pytest -q
+python -m perps.cli publish
+```
+
+> Tipp: Wenn `pre-commit` im PATH fehlt, nutze immer `python -m pre_commit ...`
+
+## Ordner
+```
+src/perps/            # Paket
+docs/                 # Artefakte (Signals, index.md)
+```
+
